### Register
POST http://localhost:4000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{ "name":"Aman","email":"student1@example.com","password":"password123","preferredLanguage":"pa","region":"Punjab","grade":5 }

### Login
POST http://localhost:4000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{ "email":"student1@example.com","password":"password123" }

### List lessons (paste token)
GET http://localhost:4000/api/lessons?grade=5
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Adapt one lesson (replace LESSON_ID)
GET http://localhost:4000/api/lessons/adapted/LESSON_ID?language=pa&region=Punjab&grade=5
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Progress
POST http://localhost:4000/api/progress
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{ "lessonId":"LESSON_ID","status":"completed","score":0 }

### Context events
GET http://localhost:4000/api/context/events
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
